No person shall, on or after the commencement of this Act, assume for the purposes of business, or be registered in terms of the Companies Act, under—
(a) a name which includes with the word "airline" or "airways" the word or words "Central African", "national", "Malawi", "Malawian", "Rhodes", "Rhodesia", "Rhodesian", "state", "Zambia" or "Zambian"; or
